column5: Was a great day had by all. Weather couldn't have been better. We had 87 contestants that signed up for the derby. Winners were Kiven that took home $400.00 for first place, then Collin $240.00 for 2nd. and Kristin $160.00 for 3rd. Congrats to the winners.              Kiven, Collin, Kristin.
Nice weather indeed  Thanks for sharing.
looks like a good time! thanks for sharing
